Another for pain in the stomach. Take myrrh and powder it as best you can and put it in a glass of good white wine and drink it warm. You should take a spoonful of the powder. Stay warm in bed and at the end of half an hour you will be freed and do not fail to do this because it is the way to health. Also take the herb water germander and make 2 pancakes and eat these warm in the morning early and soon you will be cured.

